    "description": "<strong>帮助弗兰克穿越历史，进入奇异的梦境世界！</strong><br>收集资源，获得盟友，建造塔楼，抵御一波波独特的敌人。面对穴居人的部落、法国士兵的军团或中世纪的骑士。解放你的同学，扩大你的爪牙，利用他们的帮助，走出这飘飘欲仙的睡眠。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/efcc25834183fa31553e9f374bc8f360.poster.avif?t=1769613152\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/efcc25834183fa31553e9f374bc8f360.webm?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/efcc25834183fa31553e9f374bc8f360.mp4?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >经典塔防</h2></strong>有塔的地方就一定有一波又一波的敌人! 穿越六个不同的历史时期。在你的路上，你会遇到伟大的战士和领导人，他们将自己写在历史的书页上，当然是以稍微改变的形式。这个世界充满了奇怪的和恶魔般的生物。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/79b6ed236dbd4b8ab9d15c86b45c5d8a.poster.avif?t=1769613152\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/79b6ed236dbd4b8ab9d15c86b45c5d8a.webm?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/79b6ed236dbd4b8ab9d15c86b45c5d8a.mp4?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >塔楼、升级和小兵</h2></strong>收集木材和石头等资源来建造和升级防御塔楼。除了弹弓之外，它们将是你对抗对手的主要防御手段。在战斗中使用你的帮手，给他们分配简单的任务，保卫你的基地<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/081f163612204dc99c6e61205facfcca.poster.avif?t=1769613152\" width=600 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/081f163612204dc99c6e61205facfcca.webm?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1563870/extras/081f163612204dc99c6e61205facfcca.mp4?t=1769613152\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作和单人游戏模式</h2></strong>在这个疯狂的世界里，无论是单人还是与你的一群最好的朋友一起开始这个惊人的冒险。",
